summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 220E, page 6, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Portion of Lots 1, 2, 3, Block 52, H. E. Orr Park, located at the northwest corner of E. 125th St. and 10th Ave. N.E., as Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
